        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a <hi rend="italic">Corydalis</hi>.</p>  
<p>Hermann Crüger’s paper [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4394</hi>] splendid, but he has made a mess of propagating <hi rend="italic">Cinchona</hi> in Trinidad.</p> 
            <p>JDH’s opinion of Germans.</p>
